column1: moreau-broto autocorrelation of lag 8 weighted by atomic number
column2: moreau-broto autocorrelation of lag 0 weighted by intrinsic state
column3: moran coefficient of lag 6 weighted by sanderson en

column5: 4-ordered averaged chi path weighted by valence electrons
